    • getOutputEnabledDelta

      public OutputEnabledDelta getOutputEnabledDelta()
      Additions/subtractions of outputs for the experiment supplied by the user.

      These are applied to an existing source of output-enabled rules (e.g. defaults from a task, or rules defined in the experiment's OutputManager.

    • getInputFilterExtensions

      public Optional<Set<String>> getInputFilterExtensions()
      If defined, a set of extension filters that can be applied on inputDirectory

      A defined but empty set implies no check is applied

      An Optional.empty() implies no extension filters exist.

    • setInputFilterExtensions

      public void setInputFilterExtensions​(Optional<Set<String>> inputFilterExtensions)
      If defined, a set of extension filters that can be applied on inputDirectory

      A defined but empty set implies no check is applied

      An Optional.empty() implies no extension filters exist.
